Client-http://www.mediafire.com/?a2n00z2lfv1v37w Source-http://www.mediafire.com/?1uiyd97f1zadk9d
To change the ip to yours in the client go to client.jar in your client search for "zach-scape.no-ip.biz" replace with "Your ip" :) hope i helped ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ ~ENJOY!~
Hello everyone this is my first Source, so dont go to crazy on me.. ;) Story--~~I once hosted this server with well over 25+ ppl a day but i quit because no one would donate towards the vps or vbulliten so i pretty much said fuck it. ~~Features~~ ~Working d claw spec 100% ~working pest control ~Rewards point system ~moved home to edge ~moved all shops to edge ~added theiving stalls at home ~added prayer altar lunar altar and ancients altar at home ~you now do ::slayer to get to slayer tower and do ::gwd to get to godwars ~All gwd bosses ~staff of light ~(i) rings ~imbued~ ~rock crabs training (1500 exp per hit -- go to "Config" to change the exp rate per hit ~lots of commands ~working fight pits mini ~Castle wars is 30% you can fix the rest ~working veng :D ~working clan chat ~Barrows mini works 100% - just like real rs ~Pretty good switching and no bank glitches ~chaotics ~turmoil - 100% --Shitty pi emote though :( ~All pvp armours and weapons ~Staking works at ::duelarena ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- [URL=http://img189.imageshack.us/i/clawsa.png/][IMG]http://img189.imageshack.us/img189/4329/clawsa.th.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://img860.imageshack.us/i/turmoil.png/][IMG]http://img860.imageshack.us/img860/4117/turmoil.th.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://img233.imageshack.us/i/homewx.png/][IMG]http://img233.imageshack.us/img233/8149/homewx.th.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://img98.imageshack.us/i/vengs.png/][IMG]http://img98.imageshack.us/img98/1011/vengs.th.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://img535.imageshack.us/i/stakingworks.png/][IMG]http://img535.imageshack.us/img535/3756/stakingworks.th.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://img200.imageshack.us/i/chaoticlong.png/][IMG]http://img200.imageshack.us/img200/1304/chaoticlong.th.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://img843.imageshack.us/i/chaoticmaul.png/][IMG]http://img843.imageshack.us/img843/5999/chaoticmaul.th.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://img861.imageshack.us/i/chaoticrapier.png/][IMG]http://img861.imageshack.us/img861/7969/chaoticrapier.th.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://img62.imageshack.us/i/donatorshop.png/][IMG]http://img62.imageshack.us/img62/2545/donatorshop.th.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://img96.imageshack.us/i/trainja.png/][IMG]http://img96.imageshack.us/img96/927/trainja.th.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://img231.imageshack.us/i/itemsh.png/][IMG]http://img231.imageshack.us/img231/9458/itemsh.th.png[/img][/URL] ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- Credits ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- zach (me) extreme ~~~~~~~~ If you have any questions go ahead and ask i will answer ASAP
